So Haylee Erickson and Pat Lawson both passed away the other night. Once again it was because of drinking and driving. I am so upset about it. i am just gald that I got to get to know haylee again. She and i didn't get along too much when we first met but I am glad that i got the opertunity to get to know her. I will always miss you girl. Pat i have known since i was in 4th grade and i went out with him twice. I have so many great memories about him. my prayers are with both of them. I hope that they are in a better place.



Love Always and Forever,
Iesha May Bliss

So I haven't been on here in a long time. I just thought I would update. I haven't really been seeing anyone since Oliver. I don't know what's wrong with me but guys don't seem to like me anymore. I am not going back to school to get my diploma, I am probably going to wait a while and go to a comunity college. I am probably moving to Vancover WA as soon as my transfer comes in for work. Oh yeah, I work at Check Into Cash now. Well, I better go cause I have work in the morning. If anyone still uses this, leave me a note.

Iesha

Hey whats up? Im just sittin here hanging out with a couple of my friends and thought I would update real quick. I finally made a doc appt. and its on tuesday so once again I am going to be leaving school early again. I hope they have some good news for me. I don't know, I just wish that I could finally start feeling healthy. Anyways, I guess I am gonna go. write again at a later time. Leah, give me a call. 752-0655

So Graduation is coming up fast. I can't beleive that there is only one more week of school and then we are out! I have decided that insead of doing summer school I am going to be coming back next year and just doing a lab class. I think that will work out better for me. I really have a bad head ache but I can't even go home right after school, I have to go over to Sarah's so that I can work on some stuff for citizenship with her. Well, I guess I just wanted to update. Later

So some of you have already heard this story but I figured I'd write about it and maybe I would feel a litle bit better. I have been hanging out with Chris (Oliver, my ex's, roomate) and I had started to like him a little bit. He kept on telling me that he wanted to talk to me about something but he was too chickenshit to tell me. Then the other night I was over at his house and he kissed me. That was what he wanted to talk to me about. I had brought Renee with me to meet everyone and everything was going great. Renee and I had been hanging out in Chris's room and I told Chris by and I told Renee to get her stuff and lets go. I walked into the living room and sayed bye to everyone and then I saw that Renee hadn't followed me so I went back into Chris's room and found her on his bed. Then she rolled on top of him. I thought she was just playing around so I said "get your stuff lets go" then I walked out of the room. She still wasn't following me so I went back in there and she was still on top of him. I got pissed and told her if she didn't come right then that I was leaving her. God, she pissed me off so bad! Then I drove her home in silence and went home. Chris had called me so I called him back and we got in a fight. I don't really want to go on about that right now but I called him yesterday before school and left a message telling him that I may ahve overreacted and to call me so we can talk things out. He didn't call me last night and I went to hang out with Oliver last night and by the time I had gotten to his house, Chris was already asleep so I couldn't really talk to him. I am going to give him a call right after school and hopefully we can talk. I will update you guys on what happens with that. I also have to make a doctors appt. after school to finaly get checked to see if I have an ulcer. Well, I guess I am going to go. HAPPY BIRTHDAY LEAH!!! P.S. You guys never respond to anything anymore. Please do the little word thing that I posted last time.

Meh, I miss my kitty! I really do. I wish that I could just drive by my old motel and she would just be there waiting for me to come get her. I think I might go look for her again before I go home today. The choir concert was last night and I think that the Trebal choir has improved so much this year. We listened to the old concerts taht we have done and we listened to last nights concert and I am so proud of the people in our class who have worked so hard and improved so much. Anyways, enough about that. Graduation is coming up and I wish I could be up there with everyone else walking and getting a diploma. But atleast I will be there to share the day with everyone else. Well, I guess I am going to end this. Laterz

That would be an awsome job but if they put me on part time then I don't think I am going to eccept the job. It doesn't even start till the 13 of next month and it is only 2 days a week. Well, I am going to go. I have to go back to my classroom.

Ok, I'm going to start by asking, does this icon not fit me or what?!?! Lol. Anyways, I am now it an apartment. I get a room all to myself which is very nice. I have been seeing Jon Miles latley and we decided that we would just see where things go...but then I went to his house yesterday and it kind of seemed like he has been seeing this girl named Chrissy (she was there) it seemed like he was trying to avoid her so that she wouldn't touch him or anything. I dont' know, maybe I am just being paranoid but it seemed like somthing was up. I dunno. My cat is still missing and I am going to put up lost signs for her today. I hope I am able to find her. And I hope that if I find her I get to keep her. Well, anyways, just thougth I would catch up a little. My phone is going to be hooked back up on thursday and it will be the same number.

Everything is just so fucked up! I am so sick of life and everything that comes along with it. One thing after the other just keeps getting fucked up. First I lost my house. Than I started fighting with my family. Then Oliver and I broke up. Then my sister and I started fighting. Then my cat ran away and now I can't find her and even if I do I probably wont be able to keep her cause my mom is going to move into a place that doesn't eccept pets. Why the fuck can't anything go right? I am so close to ending all of it. I don't want to but if it is the only way out then so be it. Well, I geuss I am going to go.

So Senior Prom was pretty lame. I got there at like 9:00 and stayed till about 10:00. My date was Sara Smith. It was pretty fun hanging out with her again. After prom we went to Jon Miles house and hung out with him, Scooter, Sanchez, Eric Bade, Josey, and I think there might be a couple of other people that I am forgetting about. Anyways, that was fun too! We did a little bit of drinking and Eric and Jon did a little air guitar and singing for Sara and I and then Jon put on my dress and tiara and walked around the house. I had a good time and I can't wait to see what the pictures look like. Well anyways, Oliver and I talked. We both ended up crying and he told me that he still had feelings for me he just doesn't know what he wants right now. I don't know if that means that there is still a chance with him or not. I know that I should just forget him but I really do care for him and I really want to be with him. Last night Jon asked if we could date. I told him no and that Oliver and I just broke up and I'm not over him and that another reason is that him and his girlfriend just broke up because he cheated on her with Oliver's sister. I don't think that I could really ever trust him cause of knowing that. Plus, I'm not really all that attracted to him. Well, I think that I am going to go. Please leave me notes!!!! I noticed that not too many people write on here anymore.

So I got a dress from Blue Skies For Children. They have a formal loan program so that you don't have to go buy one, you can borrow one. I got this white dress with gold in it and I am going to look like a bride. Anyways, yesterday one of the people that works there (Kristin) and another girl who I hadn't met that works there (Carrie) met up with me at Payless Shoes and they got me some shoes to go with the dress and then baught me a purse to go with my dress and a neclace and earing set plus a camera. It was a lot of fun. I don't know if prom will be fun or not but I hope it isn't stupid like all the rest of the dances are. After prom, Sara and I are going to go to Jon Miles house to hang out with him and Scooter. That should be fun. Well, I am going to go. Later.

So I am just assuming that Oliver and I are over now. I don't know what to do other than to call him but he wont answer my calls and wont return text messages. I just feel like shit in general. I feel so overwhelmed and I think I am going to start taking the rest of my Zoloft. I know that it is just going to skrew with me in the end but at least it will help me for the time being. Any of you who actually know me know that I haven't been this depressed in a long time. I hate it. I hate being bitchy and snaping at people for nothing just because I am depressed. Anyways, I guess that I better get some work done so that I don't have to spend too much time in summer school.

So I really don't have any fucking idea what is going on in my life anymore and I am starting to not care. Everything is just so shitty that I am once again dreaming about suicide. I feel like I am sufficating, like life is just a bag over my head not letting me breath. What the hell am I supposed to do? Oliver isn't returning my calls and I think that it is over between us. I guess the prince was really a toad. My family does nothing but fight with the exception of my dad and I which is really fucking unbeleiveable. I am not going to get to walk with everyone else, I don't have a dress for prom and I probably wont even fit into the one that I wore last year which I need to get from Sarah still. I don't know. Everything is just so depressing. HELP!!!!!!

So everything between Oliver and I is fine now. I moved out of his house because it was really putting a wear on our relationship now. Well, I G2G but I just wanted to post real quick. Later!

My prince charming is turning out to be a toad! I already wrote on here about how this girl named Jenie kissed Oliver and he said that in some strange way, he wanted her. Well, last night I went to Oliver's house cause thats were I am staying right now and she was there with her friend and Jared was also there. I sat there for about an houre watching him just stare at her and Jared was the only one talking to me. Then I went to watch TV and Jared watched it with me and I went to go get stuff for dinner and made us dinner (Oliver and I) and he didn't even say thank you at first. He told me thank you later on after he had gotten drunk. He barely said two words to me pretty much the whole night and then I woke up this morning and he wasn't there. I text messeged him today and he went over to Jeni's house last night. WTF!?!?! I don't know what to do. I really like this guy but I don't think I can take this. And the worse part is that he didn't even pick up on me being mad at him last night. Well, I guess I am going to go. I am in school right now and I really should be doing some work.
Please ignor that last entry. It was for school.

The Websters Dictionary Discribes euthanasia as " the act or practice of killing or permitting the death of hopelessly sick or injured individuals in a relatively painless way for reasons of mercy." In other words, putting people out of their missory, which is what they would be going through.
	On youdebate.com a poll was taken, the question was "Should euthanasia be leagal?"61% said yes. On another poll by National Opinion Polls, 79% said that they should change the laws to allow euthanasia to be legal. Around the world, other countries are for euthanasia too. The Dutch parlement legalized euthanasia in April of 2001. Polls showed that 90% of the 
public are for euthanasia.
	If someone is suffering and wants to die, they should be allowed to die. Who really wants to live when they have to go through so much pain and suffering. It is more humane to let the person die rather than make them live and have to go through torture. On top of that it must be really hard to keep on living if you know that you are going to die. If I knew that I was going 
to die, I would rather just get it over with than to keep on living in agony. 
	Other people have the arugument that what if the person can't communicate. Well, that also goes with the fact that they are being tortured. They have to go on day by day without the ability to communicate how much pain they are in. There is also the factor that people who are terminal are going to die in the end. The people that are having to take care of them are also having to pay for them to stay in hospitals and take so much of their time taking care of the person. It may be a selfish way to look at things, but it is also rational and reality. 
	Technically there are two types of Euthanasia. Voluntary and Involuntary. Voluntary is when the person gives rational, persistant, and voluntary consent. Involuntary is when the person is unable to communicate to let people know their wishes. I am for both of them. I think that is 
should be up to the main care giver to decide whether the person is suffering enough to die in the situation of involuntary euthanasia. That person should know the person well enough to know their wishes.
	A way to help this problem with whether euthanasia is wanted or unwanted would be to make it so that when you are an adult, it would be manditory to make a living will stating whetheror not you would like to have euthanasia performed if you are unable to communicate. Of courseyour opinion may change so it should be allowed to be changed at any point in time.
	In all, I think that Euthanasia should be permitted whether is it voluntary or involuntary. Keep in mind that you are helping someone to end the suffering that they are going through. Thank you!

So an update on how my spring break has been going. My birthday was ok. I had a party over at my boyfriends house and that was pretty fun. Brittany and Sarah and Megan and Shelly all were there although, Brittany left early to hang out with Ian and didn't call me back later like she said she was going to, *Eh Hem* Anyways, My mom picked me up from there at around 3 and then the next day we had another birthday party at my house for close family and friends. That was fun, My sis kept on making me take shots with her. I was hoping that I was going to be able to get my licens this spring break but it looks like I am only going to be able to take the written and I will have to take the drive test after break. Well, I gotta go but Leave me notes!!!! TTYL

Happy St. Patricks Day Everyone!!! So, Mr. Clark won the Principal Of The Year Award the year. He really does deserve it! I am being picked up after school today by Jason (neighbor) And we are going to be hanging out for pretty much the whole day. There is a St. Patricks Day party at his house tonight so that should be fun. Meh, the only problem is that I am kind of tired even though I went to bed early last night. Well, I better go. Later!

Well, I am less confused about things but I am still a little confused. I decided that I am finally going to let Matt go and that I am going to give Jason a try. He is really sweet and, even though I am afraid that I am going to somehow hurt him, I think I want to be with him. So that is that, I am going to pack up all the stuff that Matt ever gave to me with the exception of the raindeer beani baby back to him. But yeah, I think that I have to get back to my work so I will write again soon.

Yesterday started off with my mom waking me up at 9:00 in the morning asking me if I wanted to go have breakfast with her. When we got home I called Jason to let him know that I was home and to call me when he was getting up so that we could hang out. Then t 10:30 I was going to take a nap but Renee called me and I went to help her paint the walls of her old house and then we got back to her house and I waited for Jason for like 3 hours.  When he finally picked me up we went to the horseshoe and had some coffee and then I thought that we should go have a picknick at Lake Padden so we invited Jason and Clare to come along too. The plan was that we were going to have the picknick and then be back at the horseshoe to pick Oli up at 6:00 then go do something. But we were late picking up Oli and saw him walking so we went back to his house like he told us to and hung out there for the rest of the night at the party that was going on at his house. I drank quite a bit and then did somthing I might regret. I let Jason (not my best friend Jason, his neighbor) kiss me. I am still hung up on Matt for some stupid reason and I don't want to hurt Jason, I mean, I really like him but I don't want him to have to suffer because I am so stupid. So I am a little confused about that. Anyways, Clare was also having fun playing with my boobs the whole time. This morning I woke up and got dressed and woke my mom up so that she could take me to get laytex gloves for my speech thing and we ran into Jan, Dan's wife. I don't know if anyone remembers when I talked about Dan and how he died a little while back but his daughter just had a baby boy. I almost started crying cause I know that he will never be able to hold or play with him or anything. Dan was so happy when he found out that Jill was pregnant and I am almost in tears now knowing what could have been if he had been able to live. I think I am going to end this now so that I don't start crying. Later.

Of course Jason had to tell me that he was using Mary(sorry, she goes by Molly now) as a pillow. Shows that he cares a lot and is still planing on us getting back together huh? I told him that I couln't stand her and he told me to give her a chance so I did and then he got what I ment about her. We ended up ditching her. LOL! Stupid bitch! So last night I went to bed after watching a movie at about 11:00 and I figured that I would get about 6-7 hours of sleep and I would be good. Well, that idea went out the window. Apparently, my sister called last night first and told my mom that she was getting evicted so we don't know if she and my two neices are going to be staying with us or not. Then, Mark (a family friend) called and wanted my mom to pick him up. This would have been all good but my mom and dad woke me up getting ready to go. Then, after I had finally fallen asleep, Mark and my mom came home and woke me up again. I decided this mornign that I would miss first period so that I could get another hour and half sleep. But yeah, that was my sucky night. Today I woke up with a migrain and I still have one. Well, I guess I am going to go. Later.

Last night my family and I went to dinner at The Mongolian Grill and then we went and saw the movie Cursed. It was an awsome movie and an awsome night. It was like my family actually loved and like each other. There was no fighting and it was all I could ever hope for. I was talking to my mom this morning and we were talking about moving n' stuff and she told me that she had also been looking at studio apartments and that when the time comes for me to move out, she will help me get a studio apartment. Ever since that one night that my sister, my mom, and I all sat down and talked, things between my mother and I have been so much better. I am glad that we had that talk. I dunno. I am really tired right now and I can't wait to get home and take a nap. My head is hurting too and I think I am getting a migrane. I am trying to get my old middle school choir teacher to come to the upcoming concert but it doesn't look like he is going to be able to go. Well, I guess I am going to end this. Later.

So, yeah, my ex called me the other night and I didn't know it but he now lives in Florida. I don't know what to think about that and I don't even know if I really want to talk to him. Last time I really talked to him, I was still mad at him for showing up drunk to my choir concert and missing me perform. I dunno. Leah...I am really sorry about your gradnpa. If you ever ever need to talk to someone, I am always here and you should know that. I might try and give you a call tonight. I am in lab right now and I am just waiting for class to get over. Is is just me or does the last class of the day just seem to take forever? Brandon is picking me up after school and I am going to help him and Renee get packed up to move. They found a place on Superior street off of Alabama. Well I guess I am going to go and find something to keep me occupied for the next hour and 15 min.

There is still 23 minutes untill school is over. I want to hurry up and get home so that I can take a nap. I am soooo tired! This Mono is really kicking my ass. So last night, I was in my room trying to take a nap at like 6:00 and I wake up to my dad and my brother fighting. I guess it got pretty physical too. My brother told my dad that if he didn't leave, he was going to call the cops on him. I thought that was pretty funny cause if they found out that dad was living in the house with Barry and Mom, Barry and Mom would get in trouble too cause of the restrainign order. I thought it was all pretty stupid and I just kept my mouth shut and tried not to get involved. I don't know what is going to happen. It is my dad's birthday tommorow so I don't know if my mom and I are still going to go get him a birthday present. Why does my family have to be so fucked up? Why can't we all just get along and maybe just not talk to eachother. That way, none of us will have a reason to argue with each other. My head is really starting to hurt. I should be doing my lab work but I am having a hard time concentrating on anything school wise right now. I might have my sister help me with the summaries and that way I can get them over pretty fast. I don't know what is up with Jason. His phone is dissconnected and I don't know how to get ahold of him. He is also supposed to be doing the global history for me so that I can just get it over with. Well, I guess I am going to go now and maybe read. Later
